Clover: My lady!?

Clover: How could...
Lazer: They're all dead...
Lazer: ...We just missed it.

Lazer: Whoever is left in the struggle for the throne.
Lazer: I'll see if anyone is still alive. Wait here...
Andrew: Is anyone home!?
Clover: Is he...trying to break down the door?
Andrew: It's Andrew Juliano Gomez.
Andrew: Open the door!!!
Devious: Andrew, sir! What are you doing!?
Lazer: ......

Lazer: Lock the door and wait for my signal.
Clover: Godfather, what are you thinking?
Clover: We ought to be getting aid to the survivors...
Lazer: Too late. I can only save you.
Andrew: I really miss this place...I often came here as a child. It was so busy then~ ...shops everywhere.
Clover: ......
Andrew: I'm so sorry. The tragedy that occurred a few days ago...I ought to leave you in peace.
Clover: It's fine. You were kind enough to take me in.
Clover: Although I'm not sure of your motives, thank you.
Andrew: You mean why did I let you stay here, feed you...and not kill you?
Clover: ...I'm the only one left. As soon as I die, you'll ascend to the throne. Why...
Andrew: Because your the only member of the Juan family left.
Andrew: Diana, in my eyes you're still just a child. And I am your uncle.
Clover: But——
Andrew: Of course, the issue of the throne must be resolved. But before that, I must take care of my guest~
Smuggler: Andrew Gomez! I finally got you!
Smuggler: The nobles are in charge. You dare mess with us?
Andrew: You mean the ones that took your bribes?
Andrew: They let smuggling in, destroying the nation's economy. With the Snake God as my witness, I was being generous by not killing them all.
Smuggler: Save it! Today We'll teach you what it means to stand in the way of someone's income!
Clover: (Crap, can't let Andrew find out I can battle...got to distract them!)
Clover: (Right here——!)
Andrew: Diana, are you okay!?
Clover: I was just hiding...
Clover: Do these sorts of "accidents" happen often?
Andrew: The struggle for the throne has gone on for ten years. The final stage is right here on this desolate, bleak street.
Andrew: I want to save this nation, Diana.
Clover: ......
Clover: ...It's my country too. I also want to save it.
Andrew: We can't keep this up.
Andrew: ...Are you willing to sacrifice yourself for your country, Diana?
